import React, { useState } from "react"; import { Container, Typography, Paper, Box, Button, Avatar, Grid, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, Card, CardContent, Link, Divider, } from "@mui/material"; import { green, grey } from "@mui/material/colors"; import BookmarkBorderIcon from "@mui/icons-material/BookmarkBorder"; import QuizIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Quiz"; import ReportProblemIcon from "@mui/icons-material/ReportProblem"; import ChatBubbleOutlineIcon from "@mui/icons-material/ChatBubbleOutline"; const UserProfile = () => { const [user] = useState({ username: "nikhil13", name: "Nikhil", email: "nikhil@example.com", dob: "1900-01-01", mobile: "", gender: "", city: "", country: "", activities: [ { type: "Logged in", time: "2025-03-26 20:05:50", ip: "103.81.93.51" }, { type: "Logged in", time: "2025-03-20 14:00:12", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Logged out", time: "2025-03-20 14:00:02", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Security Answer updated", time: "2025-03-20 13:51:48", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Logged in", time: "2025-03-20 13:50:51", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Account Created", time: "2025-03-20 13:50:29", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, ], }); return ( 🔓 Profile: {user.name} Home > Profile > View {/* Account Section */} Account Click here to go to the page you were on before logging in. 👨‍💼 {user.username} Learner {[ { label: "Bookmarks", icon: , count: 0 }, { label: "Answers", icon: , count: 0 }, { label: "Tests", icon: , count: 0 }, { label: "Reports", icon: , count: 0 }, ].map((item, index) => ( {item.icon} {item.label} {item.count} ))} Password Change password Change security answers {/* Personal Details Section */} Personal Details ✏️ Edit Name: {user.name} Email: {user.email} Mobile: {user.mobile || "-"} Gender: {user.gender || "-"} DOB: {user.dob} City: {user.city || "-"} Country: {user.country || "-"} About Me ✏️ Edit 📈 {/* Recent Activities */} Recent Activities # Type Time IP {user.activities.map((activity, index) => ( {index + 1}. {activity.type} {activity.time} {activity.ip} ))}
); }; export default UserProfile;
